Class Parcel

  • java.lang.Object
    • Parcel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Parcel
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The class Parcel represents a parcel object containing the recipient information, items, parcel index, parcel number and whether it is insured or not.
